author: wrowe
msg: Solve the versioning problem the old fashioned way.  Clearly nobody's
maintaining this branch, so hardcoding the current 5 year old version
number in lib/expat.h.in shouldn't be a hardship, and hardcode the
VERSION tag as moved around by automake'ish stuff into the .dsp's,
the correct VERSION tag no less.
